Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,이번에는 이렇게 뒤로도 간다.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.80,0:00:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,뒤로도?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.48,0:00:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,이렇게?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.54,0:00:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,뒤로도?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.34,0:00:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,뒤돌아서.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.94,0:00:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,거꾸로.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.98,0:00:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,뒤돌아서 가보자.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.72,0:00:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,여기 보고.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.86,0:00:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,거꾸로.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.64,0:00:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,여기 보세요.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.94,0:00:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,여기 밑에 보고 가요.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.40,0:00:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,자, 가보자.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.82,0:00:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,어구 됐어요?
