Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,잘했어요.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.52,0:00:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,한 번 더.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.78,0:00:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,한 번 더.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,한 번 더 해볼까?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.24,0:00:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,한 번 더.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.64,0:00:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,한 번 더.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.46,0:00:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,한 번 더.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.82,0:00:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,이렇게 간다.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.72,0:00:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,한 번 더.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.86,0:00:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,이렇게 뒤로 가네.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.44,0:00:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,한 번 더 해봐.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.38,0:00:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,도윤이 여기 가서 해봐.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.42,0:00:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,도윤이 저기 와서 해봐.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.60,0:00:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,할 수 있어 도윤이 잘하던데?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.38,0:00:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,도윤이 엄청 잘하던데?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.64,0:01:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,여기서 보자.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.76,0:01:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,엄청 잘하던데?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.18,0:01:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,같이 갈까 그러면?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.88,0:01:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,네.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.92,0:01:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,우리 저기 봐볼까 그러면?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,발 들기 해보자.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,발 들기. 저기 거울 봐봐.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.14,0:01:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,도윤이 어딨나?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.34,0:01:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,여기 내려와서.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.86,0:01:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,도윤이 발 들어봐.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.00,0:01:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,하나 둘 이렇게 해보자
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.28,0:01:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,발 들고 발 들어주세요
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,하나 둘 셋 넷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.90,0:01:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,해볼까? 이제 다시 해볼까?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.44,0:01:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,여기서 자 시작
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.62,0:01:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,하나 여기는 풍신에서 여기 바닥에 딱딱한 데서
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.30,0:01:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,자 하나 해보자
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.58,0:01:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,발 들어보세요
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.64,0:01:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,하나 발 들어요
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.00,0:01:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,네 그렇지
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.82,0:01:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,하나 둘 셋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.58,0:01:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,어구 잘했어요.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,다시 해보자.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.44,0:01:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,다시.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.74,0:01:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,양팔 벌리고.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.00,0:01:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,발 들어보세요.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.06,0:01:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,여기 이 발 들어주세요.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.16,0:02:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,선생님이 한번 볼까?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.58,0:02:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,여기 봐볼까?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.72,0:02:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,여기 선생님 주세요.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.60,0:02:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,발 주세요. 발.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.26,0:02:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,이렇게. 하나.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.32,0:02:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,둘. 셋. 넷.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.44,0:02:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,이렇게 해볼거에요. 해볼까?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.10,0:02:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,발 주세요. 발.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.70,0:02:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,하나.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.96,0:02:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,그렇지. 또.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.46,0:02:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,자 들어보자
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,우와 발 들어요
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.64,0:02:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,하나 둘 셋 넷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.88,0:02:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,어우 잘했어요
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,이번엔 이쪽 발도 들어볼게요
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.34,0:02:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,이쪽 발도 들어보자
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.96,0:02:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,이렇게 이렇게 드는거야
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.24,0:02:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,자 또 여기 발 들어보세요
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,여기 줘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.94,0:02:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,이 발
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.72,0:02:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,반대쪽 발 주세요
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.02,0:02:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,자 그렇지
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.50,0:02:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,하나 발 들어
