Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.74,0:03:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,이쪽에서 공 뻥 차 봐.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.92,0:03:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,뻥!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,뻥 차야지.
